From wet to styled in 30 minutes ⏱️ - here’s how:

Using the Limited Edition Shark FlexStyle in Lilac Frost 💜:

1. Blow dry freshly washed hair to 80/90% dry using the Air Styler- this is important!
2. Add the Auto-Wrap Curler attachment 
3. Hold a section of hair, bring the barrel behind the section and let the hair wrap itself around the barrel
4. Hold for 10 seconds then press the Cool Shot button for a further 10 seconds
5. Turn off the Air Styler and pull the barrel down to reveal the curl
6. Repeat over the rest of your hair
7. Don’t forget to switch the barrel when you do the other side of your head!
